sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User/Agent
    participant C as CLI
    participant S as Scaffold Engine
    participant A as AI Layer

    U->>C: foundryspec init [project-name]
    C->>S: Create "foundryspec/" folder
    S->>S: Populate exhaustive category assets
    S->>S: Write foundry.config.json (commented categories)
    S->>S: Auto-setup .gitignore & package.json
    C->>A: Generate Initial Instructions
    A->>A: Create .agent/workflows/
    C-->>U: Project Scaffolded Successfully
